Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Minutes to M1 & Smith Street Motorway

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to present 15 Jade Drive, Molendinar for sale at $1,550,000 + GST. 

This high clearance industrial warehouse is suitable to a large variety of industrial users. Ideally located within the Molendinar industrial precinct provides businesses with easy access to the M1 Motorway and Smith Street Molendinar in a matter of minutes. 

The property features: 

-	650sqm of total building area 
-	1,500sqm of land area 
-	High clearance warehousing 
-	Multiple large sliding warehouse doors 
-	Access to 3 phase power 
-	Easy access to major arterial's

Available now for inspections. 

Contact exclusive agents for further information.

- Area: 284sqm*

- Good truck access
- Ample parking
- Available now!
